{"tid":2301712,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第43屆十大中文金曲","createTime":"2020-11-26T13:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T12:01:13.000Z","uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"255a8f73f4e53d6fe11fa41754c9a37091879c6e","tid":2301712,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"第43屆十大中文金曲<br />\n<br />\n音樂─我們共通的語言。<br />\n音樂說─我們共鳴的故事。<br />\n2020年，一場疫症使世界休止、把人們隔離。幸有音樂不止息，我們仍可憑歌寄意。<br />\n香港電台以樂壇盛事─【第43屆十大中文金曲】，向一眾音樂創作人及歌手致意，藉以嘉許他們在這樣艱難的大環境下，仍然堅持創作上乘音樂、守護本地中文流行樂壇，讓音樂說故事。<br />\n<br />\n最新消息<br />\n<br />\n「第43屆十大中文金曲」網上投票已結束！<br />\n請密切留意2021年1月公布「第43屆十大中文金曲」各獎項得主"},{"pid":"6f32ffc2aff4c192efa1afdbe922f1157409d625","tid":2301712,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CCTVB 不了</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"009847b497100538e9ce0e22f216f94f6f6e2bf7","tid":2301712,"uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f32ffc2aff4c192efa1afdbe922f1157409d625","tid":2301712,"uid":9193,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>CCTVB 不了</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"港台喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd2b2a667ba659013afe269a71e3ef179aa8112","tid":2301712,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"q"},{"pid":"23b406fd9b24a4d14497a66bb2f4a7d03096ea66","tid":2301712,"uid":53673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c